            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span><br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/b136dfacdbfad3318ad97408c84f8810_867007696159348475.png",
                "id": "talent59963",
                "key": "Swiftshatter Spear",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Swiftshatter Spear"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill </span><br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Blazing Barrier</span>.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Blazing Barrier</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span><br>Grants <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1 Shield point</span> to your active character. (Can stack. Max 3 points.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/375c5e00af78c34af064565c8c932329_5095399552381446295.png",
                "id": "talent34395",
                "key": "Blazing Blessing",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Blazing Blessing"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Blazing Barrier</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Scorching Ooyoroi</span>.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Blazing Barrier</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br>Grants <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1 Shield point</span> to your active character. (Can stack. Max 3 points.)<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Scorching Ooyoroi</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your character uses a Normal Attack:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro DMG</span> and create a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Blazing Barrier</span>.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/47b82b01f63f39b206ba0c985d5de119_4187690276705837352.png",
                "id": "talent7133",
                "key": "Crimson Ooyoroi",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Crimson Ooyoroi"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Pyro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4689287028859796994.png",
                "id": "talent35572",
                "key": "Pyro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Pyro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/30/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6308077288292169739.png",
